Company Description (as filed with the SEC)
SciClone Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ: SCLN) is a United States
("U.S.")-headquartered, China-focused, specialty pharmaceutical company with a
substantial commercial business and a product portfolio of therapies for
oncology, infectious diseases and cardiovascular disorders. We are focused on
continuing to grow our revenue and profitability. Our business and corporate
strategy is focused primarily on the People's Republic of China ("China" or
"PRC") where we have built a solid reputation and established a strong brand
through many years of experience marketing our lead product,
ZADAXIN (thymalfasin). In addition, we have an established business model with
large pharmaceutical partners to promote and sell products. We believe our sales
and marketing strengths position us to benefit from the long-term expansion of
the pharmaceutical market in China.  ... More ...  




