Our development portfolio includes potential therapeutic class leaders approved in Western markets, such as the cardiovascular drugs ANGIOMAX® and Neucardin™, and the antibiotic VIBATIV®, which could move through the regulatory process as mid-term market opportunities.
We have built this attractive portfolio through targeted and successful partnering with leading pharmaceutical and biotechnology companies, including multinational corporations and innovative biopharma companies in the US, Europe, and China.































